  "title": "SECURITY SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>YORK HOTEL (PRIVATE) LIMITED</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Support the Assistant Security Manager in leading the Security Department to maintain a safe and secure environment within the hotel. Supervise security personnel, conduct training, and manage security operations to protect guests, employees, and property.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Collaborate with the Assistant Security Manager to organize the Security Department to meet management’s security requirements and provide expert advice on security matters</li><li>Supervise security personnel to ensure compliance with operational instructions and effective performance of their duties</li><li>Assist in delivering on-the-job training to new security staff and evaluate their competency to ensure readiness for operational responsibilities</li><li>Transfer essential security knowledge and skills to security officers to enhance team capability and performance</li><li>Monitor hotel premises and perimeter to identify potential criminal activities, maintain peace, and implement appropriate remedial actions promptly</li><li>Conduct thorough investigations of incidents involving guests and employees, and prepare detailed reports to inform management decisions</li><li>Perform regular patrols of hotel grounds and perimeter to detect and deter criminal activity and ensure overall safety</li><li>Execute static security duties at key locations such as the hotel lobby and Security Office to maintain a visible security presence</li><li>Support the management of casual labour to ensure adequate staffing and operational efficiency</li><li>Provide security coverage and coordinate security operations during special functions and events to safeguard attendees and property</li></ul>",
